column5: Free to the first to reply.  Just a small thanks to all of the opinions and help i have gotten from the board over the years.
Pm me your email address and ill send you an extra electronic ticket
Christopher, I havent received your PM.  Did you want the ticket?
No I'm fine, was just saying that it was a nice gesture, I'm sure someone will take it off your hands
OK, thanks.  Ticket still up for grabs.  I bought 3 tickets in November and only used two of them...so this is an extra for anyone who is planning to go.
Great.  PM me your email address and I will send you an electronic copy you can print off and present at the door.
PM sent and edited. Thank you very much!
